[{"Code":"en","Title":"Acceptable Shopfront","Slug":"shopfront-type-all-countries","ContentType":2,"Content":"<h2 data-block-id=\"maqigjaw-qdwrf6-001\">Instruction</h2><p data-block-id=\"mctvwl3a-cqg5bk-169\">You may filter the shopfront detail for channel activation based on “<strong>Country is</strong>”. You may choose between ID, PH, MY, TH, and VN, and the shopfront acceptable detail would be shown based on the country</p><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\" data-permitted-reader-groups=\"9f0df790-187b-4514-b1da-ec79a03a5322\"><p data-block-id=\"mgga5xx0-6dxaiv-003\"><strong>Private notes</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mgga5xx0-pdxfnx-004\">asdfasdfasdf</p></section><p data-block-id=\"mgga5xx0-crez3d-005\"></p><div class=\"details-wrapper details-wrapper_rendered\" data-type=\"details-wrapper\"><details data-opened=\"true\" data-button-align=\"right\" data-details-border=\"withBorder\" data-expand-icon=\"arrow\" data-lock=\"false\"><summary><p data-block-id=\"magixxou-h1lvpk-001\"><strong>Acceptable Shopfront</strong></p></summary><div data-type=\"details-content\"><p data-block-id=\"malzfowq-me3vnf-002\">The information below is to inform merchants who have a specific shopfront to get Channel Activation activated. The shopfront only needs one of the website, apps, social media, or marketplace to be provided</p><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appTjwSn2IHh323Vn/shrhnWA2UeCHCsLbF\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"\" style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel=\"\" class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p></div></details><button class=\"details-arrow\" type=\"details\"></button></div><p data-block-id=\"maqih9pe-e664vw-005\"></p><p data-block-id=\"maqj7gkm-8yyzqu-007\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Acceptable Shopfront","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Etalase yang Dapat Diterima","Slug":"shopfront-type-all-countries","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><h2 data-block-id=\"maqigjaw-qdwrf6-001\">Instruksi</h2><p data-block-id=\"mctvwl3a-cqg5bk-169\">Anda dapat memfilter detail etalase untuk aktivasi channel berdasarkan &#x201c;<strong>Country is</strong>&#x201d;. Anda dapat memilih antara ID, PH, MY, TH, dan VN, dan detail etalase yang dapat diterima akan ditampilkan berdasarkan negara</p><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\" data-permitted-reader-groups=\"9f0df790-187b-4514-b1da-ec79a03a5322\"><p data-block-id=\"mgga5xx0-6dxaiv-003\"><strong>Catatan pribadi</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mgga5xx0-pdxfnx-004\">asdfasdfasdf</p></section><p data-block-id=\"mgga5xx0-crez3d-005\"></p><div class=\"details-wrapper details-wrapper_rendered\" data-type=\"details-wrapper\"><details data-opened=\"true\" data-button-align=\"right\" data-details-border=\"withBorder\" data-expand-icon=\"arrow\" data-lock=\"false\"><summary><p data-block-id=\"magixxou-h1lvpk-001\"><strong>Etalase yang Diterima</strong></p></summary><div data-type=\"details-content\"><p data-block-id=\"malzfowq-me3vnf-002\">Informasi di bawah ini adalah untuk menginformasikan merchant yang memiliki etalase spesifik untuk mengaktifkan Aktivasi Channel. Etalase hanya perlu menyediakan salah satu dari situs web, aplikasi, media sosial, atau marketplace</p><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appTjwSn2IHh323Vn/shrhnWA2UeCHCsLbF\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p></div></details><button class=\"details-arrow\" type=\"details\"></button></div><p data-block-id=\"maqih9pe-e664vw-005\"></p><p data-block-id=\"maqj7gkm-8yyzqu-007\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Etalase yang Dapat Diterima","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"หน้าร้านที่ยอมรับได้","Slug":"shopfront-type-all-countries","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><h2 data-block-id=\"maqigjaw-qdwrf6-001\">คำแนะนำ</h2><p data-block-id=\"mctvwl3a-cqg5bk-169\">คุณสามารถกรองรายละเอียดหน้าร้านสำหรับการเปิดใช้งานช่องทาง (channel activation) โดยอิงจาก &#x201c;<strong>ประเทศคือ</strong>&#x201d;. คุณสามารถเลือกได้ระหว่าง ID, PH, MY, TH, และ VN และรายละเอียดหน้าร้านที่ยอมรับได้จะแสดงตามประเทศที่เลือก</p><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\" data-permitted-reader-groups=\"9f0df790-187b-4514-b1da-ec79a03a5322\"><p data-block-id=\"mgga5xx0-6dxaiv-003\"><strong>หมายเหตุส่วนตัว</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mgga5xx0-pdxfnx-004\">asdfasdfasdf</p></section><p data-block-id=\"mgga5xx0-crez3d-005\"></p><div class=\"details-wrapper details-wrapper_rendered\" data-type=\"details-wrapper\"><details data-opened=\"true\" data-button-align=\"right\" data-details-border=\"withBorder\" data-expand-icon=\"arrow\" data-lock=\"false\"><summary><p data-block-id=\"magixxou-h1lvpk-001\"><strong>หน้าร้านที่ยอมรับได้</strong></p></summary><div data-type=\"details-content\"><p data-block-id=\"malzfowq-me3vnf-002\">ข้อมูลด้านล่างนี้มีไว้เพื่อแจ้งให้ร้านค้า (merchants) ที่มีหน้าร้านเฉพาะทราบ เพื่อเปิดใช้งาน Channel Activation หน้าร้านจำเป็นต้องมีเพียงอย่างใดอย่างหนึ่งจากเว็บไซต์, แอปพลิเคชัน, โซเชียลมีเดีย, หรือมาร์เก็ตเพลส เพื่อใช้ในการยื่นเรื่อง</p><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appTjwSn2IHh323Vn/shrhnWA2UeCHCsLbF\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p></div></details><button class=\"details-arrow\" type=\"details\"></button></div><p data-block-id=\"maqih9pe-e664vw-005\"></p><p data-block-id=\"maqj7gkm-8yyzqu-007\"></p>","SeoTitle":"หน้าร้านที่ยอมรับได้","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Frente de tienda aceptable","Slug":"shopfront-type-all-countries","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><h2 data-block-id=\"maqigjaw-qdwrf6-001\">Instrucción</h2><p data-block-id=\"mctvwl3a-cqg5bk-169\">Puede filtrar el detalle del escaparate para la activación de canal basándose en &#x201c;<strong>Country is</strong>&#x201d;. Puede elegir entre ID, PH, MY, TH y VN, y el detalle aceptable del escaparate se mostraría basándose en el país</p><section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\" data-permitted-reader-groups=\"9f0df790-187b-4514-b1da-ec79a03a5322\"><p data-block-id=\"mgga5xx0-6dxaiv-003\"><strong>Notas privadas</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mgga5xx0-pdxfnx-004\">asdfasdfasdf</p></section><p data-block-id=\"mgga5xx0-crez3d-005\"></p><div class=\"details-wrapper details-wrapper_rendered\" data-type=\"details-wrapper\"><details data-opened=\"true\" data-button-align=\"right\" data-details-border=\"withBorder\" data-expand-icon=\"arrow\" data-lock=\"false\"><summary><p data-block-id=\"magixxou-h1lvpk-001\"><strong>Escaparate Aceptable</strong></p></summary><div data-type=\"details-content\"><p data-block-id=\"malzfowq-me3vnf-002\">La información a continuación es para informar a los comercios que tienen un escaparate específico para obtener la activación de Canal activada. Solo se necesita proporcionar uno de los siguientes elementos del escaparate: sitio web, apps, redes sociales o marketplace</p><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appTjwSn2IHh323Vn/shrhnWA2UeCHCsLbF\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p></div></details><button class=\"details-arrow\" type=\"details\"></button></div><p data-block-id=\"maqih9pe-e664vw-005\"></p><p data-block-id=\"maqj7gkm-8yyzqu-007\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Frente de tienda aceptable","Description":null}]